OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FItalian banks hit with     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fsurprise windfall tax      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Italy has passed a one-off 40% tax on  
OL,6, the profits banks earn from higher     
OL,7, interest rates, in a shock move that   
OL,8, has seen shares plummet.               
OL,10,FA hike in official interest rates has  
OL,11,Fresulted in record profits for Italian 
OL,12,Fbanks, prompting the government's move.
OL,14,FProceeds will be used to help mortgage 
OL,15,Fholders and to cut taxes, the          
OL,16,Fgovernment says.                       
OL,18,FBut Italian banks have said the tax on 
OL,19,Ftheir profits will be "substantially   
OL,20,Fnegative" for the sector.              
